interpretation: The "girl" card represents youth, innocence, and new beginnings. This card can indicate a fresh start, a new adventure, or a new relationship. The girl is full of hope and curiosity, eager to explore the world around her. She may represent a young person in your life, or a part of yourself that is still learning and growing. This card can also suggest a need for playfulness, creativity, and a childlike sense of wonder. The girl encourages you to embrace your inner child and approach life with a sense of openness and enthusiasm.
